data.description: Only 1 year old! Refrigerator stays! Low maintenance 4-bedroom, single-story home conveniently located off Tiger Bend Road! Step inside and you will notice the expansive open concept, that is perfect for entertaining. The kitchen offers 1 year-old stainless-steel appliances, 3cm granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, gas range, a large pantry, and a generously sized island. The primary suite includes granite countertops, dual vanities, a separate shower, soaking tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. But that's not all—this home is equipped with smart home features. Backyard is larger than shown in photos. It extends further than the fence!
